 gy\, restraint.\n\nThe darkest night of the month. A time of stillness.\n
 \nSuggested focus: Do not rush into decisions. Observe. Listen.\n\nHe toh
 u: the tohu of your own taiao always take precedence over the calendar.\n
 \nTe kōrero hōhonu ake · The deeper detail: https://temaramataka.nz/
